Parma.WOIO: WOIO, virtual channel 19 (VHF digital channel 10), is a CBS-affiliated television station serving Cleveland, Ohio, United States that is licensed to Shaker Heights. The station is owned by Raycom Media, as part of a duopoly with Lorain-licensed MyNetworkTV affiliate WUAB (channel 43). The two stations share studios on the ground floor of the Reserve Square building in Downtown Cleveland and transmitter facilities in the Cleveland suburb of Parma.
